BFN 

  [Text] Havana, 27 Apr (PL) -- Jose Antonio Ocampo, 
Colombian minister of agriculture and livestock, today began an 
official visit to Cuba with the goal of entering into 
cooperation accords with the Cuban Ministry of Agriculture. 
  Ocampo, who is visiting at the invitation of Cuban 
Agriculture Minister Alfredo Jordan, declared his trip is also 
aimed at achieving technological exchanges in the area of 
biotechnology, of which he recognized Cuba's prestige throughout 
