<F P=104>  La Paz Television Nacional Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The blockading of roads on 28 April has had very 
little effect on everyday life. The Campesino Confederation of 
Bolivia issued a communique calling on brother campesinos to 
remain calm, adding that it remains expectant and hopes that the 
government will satisfy the needs of the campesino sector. 
