<F P=100> CARIBBEAN </F>
<F P=101> Cuba </F>
<H3> <TI>   Officials, Media Preview Special ANPP Session </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Officials, Media Preview Special ANPP Session </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    ANPP Commissions To Meet on 30 Apr </H4>

<F P=102> FL2904182294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1700 
GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2904182294 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The commissions of the National Assembly of the 
People's Government [ANPP] will meet in Havana on 30 April, the 
day before the special session of the ANPP. The commissions will 
meet at the Nico Lopez National School of the Communist Party of 
Cuba and at the headquarters of the ANPP to study issues related 
to their spheres of work. 
  These meetings come before the May Day special session of 
ANPP where delegates will focus on the internal economic 
situation to find solutions to the financial problems Cuba faces. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

