  [Text] One of the main promoters for the formation of a new 
government through the application of Constitution articles is 
trying to obtain popular support. On 29 April, Senator Bernard 
Sansaricq sent a call to the population to support the 
application of Article 149 of the Constitution, the only chance, 
according to him, to spare the country a social explosion. Sen. 
Sansaricq promised the populace the formation of a nationalist, 
competent government, with new people for a new start. 

