Association of Agricultural Entrepreneurs; Manuel Llosa, 
director of the Investment Bank; Carlos Reategui, a New Majority 
congressman; and Mining Society and Banking Association 
representatives. 
  Foreign Minister Goldenberg will meet his Swedish 
counterpart, Margaretha Ugglas, and hold contacts with Swedish 
banks. 
  The Peruvian minister of industry, tourism, integration, and 
commerce will meet the mission in Switzerland and Austria. 

